# /config/ Directory Structure

The `/config/` directory contains configuration files for different environments to ensure smooth deployment and scalability of the AI Virtual Therapist project.

## Directory Contents

```plaintext
/config/
├── development/          # Development environment configuration
│   ├── app_config.json   # Application-level configurations
│   ├── db_config.json    # Database connection settings
│   ├── env_variables.env # Environment variables for local dev
│   └── logging.yaml      # Logging configurations
├── production/           # Production environment configuration
│   ├── app_config.json   # Application-level configurations
│   ├── db_config.json    # Database connection settings
│   ├── env_variables.env # Environment variables for production
│   └── logging.yaml      # Logging configurations
├── staging/              # Staging environment configuration
│   ├── app_config.json   # Application-level configurations
│   ├── db_config.json    # Database connection settings
│   ├── env_variables.env # Environment variables for staging
│   └── logging.yaml      # Logging configurations
└── secrets/              # Secure storage of sensitive information
    ├── api_keys.json     # API keys and authentication details
    ├── encryption_keys.json # Encryption key storage
    └── ssh_keys/         # SSH key management
